title: ASVe, Bailo a Costantinopoli, Carte turche, reg. 250, fasc. 330 Page  15
english_summary: Order sent upon the request of the Venetian bailo regarding a group of ships (kadırga) belonging to the Venetians that crushed near the harbor of Boyana. Ships and the things that were inside confiscated by the Ottoman officials are requested to be handed over either to bey of Kotor or his men that have been sent.
agencies: İskenderiye Sancakbeyi;İskenderiye Mukataa müfettişi;Ülgün Kadısı;Bar Kadısı;Venedik balyosu
